                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280703-154-off772 t18280703-154-crimeloc774"></join>, a little after two o'clock on the 2d of July; I missed my handkerchief, turned round, and saw the prisoner putting it into his waistcoat; I seized him, and took him into a shop, where he was taken charge of.</p>
